Our Mission

To democratize AI education across Armenia by empowering educators and students with the knowledge, skills, and ethical foundation needed to thrive in the digital age.

What We Stand For

AI4ALL Armenia is more than an educational initiative—it's a movement to transform how Armenia approaches artificial intelligence. We believe that AI education should be accessible, ethical, and empowering for all.

Democratize AI Education

Make AI education accessible to all educators and students across Armenia, regardless of their location or background.

Empower Educators

Provide teachers with the tools and knowledge to integrate AI into their teaching practices effectively.

Build Future-Ready Skills

Equip young learners with essential AI skills for the digital economy and future career opportunities.

Promote Ethical AI

Emphasize human-centered, ethical AI development to ensure responsible innovation and societal benefit.

Our Vision

We envision an Armenia where every educator and student has the knowledge and tools to harness the power of artificial intelligence for positive change. A future where AI serves humanity, enhances creativity, and drives innovation while preserving our values and cultural heritage.

2025

Reach 1,000+ participants across all 11 regions of Armenia

2027

Establish AI4ALL Armenia as the leading AI education platform in the region

2030

Create a sustainable ecosystem of AI-literate educators and innovators

Our Values

These core values guide everything we do and shape how we approach AI education in Armenia.

Inclusivity

We believe AI education should be accessible to everyone, regardless of their background or location.

Innovation

We embrace cutting-edge technologies and methodologies to deliver the most effective learning experiences.

Ethics

We prioritize ethical considerations in AI development and ensure responsible use of artificial intelligence.

Community

We foster a supportive community of learners, educators, and professionals committed to AI advancement.

Excellence

We maintain the highest standards in our educational programs and continuously strive for improvement.

Collaboration

We work closely with educational institutions, government bodies, and industry partners to maximize impact.

Join Our Mission

Be part of the AI revolution in Armenia. Together, we can build a brighter, more innovative future.
